    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Google adds end-to-end Gmail encryption to Android, iOS devices for enterprises</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Google has made a big step forward by extending end-to-end encryption to Android and iOS devices for Gmail client-side encryption (CSE) users, says an expert.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2026/04/10/google-adds-end-to-end-gmail-encryption-to-android-ios-devices-for-enterprises/"  >(Computer World)</a>
    </p>
