        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Microsoft announces end of support for ASP.NET Core 2.3</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Microsoft’s ASP.NET Core 2.3, a version of the company’s open source web development framework for .NET and C#, will reach end of life support on April 7, 2027.
Following that date, Microsoft will no longer provide bug fixes, technical support, or security patches for ASP.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2026/04/08/microsoft-announces-end-of-support-for-asp-net-core-2-3/"  >(Info World)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
