    <h3 itemprop="headline">AI needs more power: Offices could be the answer</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Seattle startup Edo is helping utilities turn office buildings into virtual power plants as AI demand and extreme weather add pressure to the grid.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2026/04/06/ai-needs-more-power-offices-could-answer/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
