        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Z.ai unveils GLM-5.1, enabling AI coding agents to  run autonomously for hours</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Chinese AI company Z.ai has launched GLM-5.1, an open-source coding model it says is built for agentic software engineering. The release comes as AI vendors move beyond autocomplete-style coding tools toward systems that can handle software tasks over longer periods with less human input.
Z.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2026/04/08/z-ai-unveils-glm-5-1-enabling-ai-coding-agents-to-run-autonomously-for-hours/"  >(Computer World)</a>
